<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-08-27T11:16:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-08-27T11:16:00-05:00" n="61" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d61">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 704.7163</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Roumania</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_VCJ1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Vopicka</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucharest</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-08-27T18:00:00+01:44">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1916, 6 p. m.</hi>
                                </date>
                                <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received August 29, 9.25 a.
                                m.</hi>]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>274 [298]. Roumanian Minister for Foreign Affairs asked me just now to
                            ask the Department to take charge of Roumanian [interests] in Austria at
                            once, and also in Germany if the war between Roumania and Germany should
                            be started.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_VCJ1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Vopicka</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>